      "notes": "Idempotency guard: mark row as in-progress BEFORE calling OpenRouter. If WF4 crashes mid-execution, the row stays as 'Scoring In Progress' and is NOT re-picked up on the next poll. Manual recovery: reset Status to 'Enriched' in the sheet."
